  "title": "Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a highly organized and proactive Admin Executive to manage our e-commerce operations across platforms like Lazada, Shopee, and Shopify. If you have a knack for multitasking, customer service, and managing online orders, we want you as our team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handle administrative tasks and provide excellent customer support.</li>\n  <li>Manage and process shift orders, returns and/or exchange efficiently on our online platforms.</li>\n  <li>Respond to customer inquiries and reply to messages promptly via phone, email, chat room in a professional manner.</li>\n  <li>Resolve customer complaints, escalate the issues when necessary and follow up to ensure customer satisfaction.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with warehouse and logistics teams to ensure smooth operations.</li>\n  <li>Maintain customer records and assists with office operations to ensure smooth business functioning. Update database as required, data entry, documentation, and filing.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate and timely order fulfillment and delivery tracking. Arrange delivery route using company system. </li>\n  <li>Follow company policies and confidentiality guidelines. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Be independent in work and as part of a team.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in MS Office (Word, Excel, Outlook, etc).</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in administration or customer service is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with CRM software is a plus. </li>\n  <li>Patience and professionalism in handling customer concerns. </li>\n  <li>Strong organizational skills and attention to detail. </li>\n  <li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills for customer interaction. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Why Join Us?</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Collaborative and supportive working environment</li>\n  <li>Opportunities for growth in the fast-growing e-commerce space</li>\n  <li>Competitive salary and benefits package</li>\n  <li>Lunch meal provided on weekdays.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🕒 Working Hours:</p>\n<p>Mon - Fri (8:30 am - 6:00 pm)</p>\n<p>Sat (8:30 am - 1:30 pm)</p>",
